NAME
  awget - safe file downloader

SYNOPSIS
  awget [-f] [-q] [--sha256=HEX] <url> [file]

DESCRIPTION
  Like wget, but checks the HTTP status (a 404 body is an error, not your
  file), writes atomically (temp then rename), and can verify integrity.

OPTIONS
  -f            overwrite an existing file
  -q            quiet (no progress)
  --sha256=HEX  verify the download against a sha256 digest

EXAMPLES
  awget https://example.com/p.lua /usr/bin/p.lua
  awget --sha256=ab12... https://host/file.bin file.bin
